      "Opening your birth chart for the first time can be disorienting. Twelve houses, ten planets, coloured lines crossing in every direction: the whole thing looks more like a subway map than a key to self-knowledge. Yet reading a natal chart follows a precise logic. If you approach it step by step, starting with the most structural elements, you can extract the essentials without knowing every minor aspect by heart.",
